import React from 'react'


import { Container, View, Logo} from '../../atoms'
import { Navigation } from '../../molecules'

import knobData from "./header.knobs.json";
const { direction, items } = knobData;

const Header = ({direction}) => {

    return (
        <Container
        display="flex"
        justifyContent="space-between"
        alignItems="center"
        boxSizing="border-box"
        padding="0px 50px 0px 30px" 
        backgroundColor="#ffffff"
        boxShadow="0px 3px 6px rgba(137, 137, 137, 0.16)">
            <View>
                <Logo width="2em"/>
            </View>
            <View>
                <Navigation direction={direction} items={items.default}/>
            </View>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Header
